Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我在网上查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 真岛你也玩歌牌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然不是那种经常在玩歌牌的闲人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不用多久 我就能超越你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天太一可是连足球练习也逃掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 你真多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}あはでこのよを すくしてよとや
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相逢无片刻 只叹命将残
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 现在还不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好～!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读牌的时候 是一下也不能动的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つゆにぬれつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滴滴冷露沾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため をしからざりし…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思难从愿 不惜下黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知道的歌牌应该就像消磨时间的扑克牌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌是一种运动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,80)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(300,200)}第三首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,240)\fn@汉仪玄宋 55S\frz270\fad(300,300)}映明吉野天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在中盘送你的牌为什么要放在这里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}老师 原田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等一会 正在反省中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 原田老师是这里的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他是个对歌牌无法放手的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个发出很大声音的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是玩歌牌的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 热烈欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管别人说什么 热烈欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}老师真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算每年两次在本地区举行启蒙向的歌牌大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝诱到的人不是一个就是两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而现在竟然一下子来三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 浩君你们这班家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴增加了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}注释:ひろ和ひょろ读音相似 其中ひょろ有摇晃和瘦弱的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小晃君?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是浩! 木梨浩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你们歌牌几段了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我只记住了あ行和な行那一半而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 那是行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没记住就来这里了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们安排的是比赛形式的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无法相提并论呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话比过再说吧 小晃君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是浩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我们就来场三对三的红白战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绵谷 比了也只是会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 太一 我们不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要比的话就要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓红白战即是团体战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牌分成五十张 互相争抢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你连这种事都不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 小晃君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是放到真岛你面前的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我所负责的牌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是千早的 把它排成三行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我还没记得的牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排好的话 就开始15分钟的背诵时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背诵时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是把排好的牌的位置记住的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果记不住这个的话 想赢就很难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然自阵和敌阵都要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要记住一百个位置?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 我完全还没记住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这15分钟间去哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到外面开个作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先千早负责的牌都是「一字决胜负」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始读到む或者す时马上就能去取的牌总共有七张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的都是些あ行的「二字决胜负」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来 真岛你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分配有叫做「大山札」的「六字决胜负」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如「あさぼらけ」和「きみがため」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两张开头五个字相同的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为需要猜牌 所以就叫「大山札」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}注释：「大山」 词源来自于「山を張る」意为：押宝、预测
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛你也可以猜牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一读到相应的牌就马上去取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要取的牌里也有「五字决胜负」的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你叫我马上去取…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是拿错了牌怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都他说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}注释:这几个假名是指一字决胜负那些牌的头一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「むすめふさほせ」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还搞什么策略 绵谷你一个人跟小晃君他比不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有拖你后腿的人 不是能赢得更轻松吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想组成一个团体作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要组成一个团体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ほととぎす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曙色朦胧里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才「一字决胜负」的牌应该是由我负责取的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你那么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}きみがため はるののにいでて わかなつむ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}原上采春芽 只为献君尝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 猜错牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我拿到那边正确的牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为你拿错牌了 所以对方要送过来一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等于各方各拿一张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大山札」的牌 我也会去取的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真岛你拿错了 也能相抵消 所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么团体啊 这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全没想过要相信我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师那是发现宝物的感动姿势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个眼镜君可不是一般的水平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}むらさめの　つゆもまだひぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}骤雨频频降 枝头露未干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被抢先一步了 好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一轮我不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么实力差距如此大却还能不甘心的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西 明明没必要那么拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算绵谷说要组成团队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也根本没有期待我们做出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}あさぼらけ うじのかわぎり たえだえに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}宇治临拂晓 河滩冷雾中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我拿到正确的牌了 绵谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一张「あさぼらけ」开头的牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静心听 静心听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静心听…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふくからに あきのくさきの しおるれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枯焦怜草木 落叶逐飞蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 终于拿到一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}老师 对不起 痛不痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(407,440)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是「枯焦怜草木」开头的牌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听出「ふ」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我可是出生到现在第一次像样的取歌牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里那么多有经验的大人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然只有这孩子动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我正式取到的第一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌真让人爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前拿到牌的时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是我掉以轻心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道取「一字决胜负」的牌 我输给了千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来还是只拿到一张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只拿到五张 五张…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小晃君 啊抱歉 浩君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的名字叫什么? 要加入我们的歌牌会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入 我叫绵谷新 小学六年级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绵谷新?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是从小学一年级到小学五年级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在分年级组比赛里 每年都全国优胜的那个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起绵谷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他是八十年代七连霸的永世名人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福井绵谷始老师的孙子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你们叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全记不住歌牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背得越多就越混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要背一百张绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 但是你不是也有完全记住的牌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(464,440)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天拿到的这张「枯焦怜草木」开头的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(470,440)}ちはやふる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 就是「悠悠神代事」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绵谷说那是我名字的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟自己深切相关的牌 就能比谁都要快拿到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百人一首总共有一百首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当做能和一百个人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地跟它们和睦相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睫毛君 你怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我要上补习班…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我会来的 尽可能地来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三月份有个大赛 你们在这里努力练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大赛?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三人一队的团体战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是六年生能参加的最后的大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要参加 对吧 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赢是吧 三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个大赛 是循环赛而不是红白赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人当中就必须有两个人赢才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然会赢 千早和太一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们其中一个给我要赢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是特训
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为早上有个广告选秀 所以花了一笔买回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早真的是姐姐的第一号粉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还会说「我的梦想是姐姐成为日本第一的模特儿」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有自己想要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}こぬひとを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}思君终不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}やくやもしほの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}卤水釜中沸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得她对一件事情有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她一点优点都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只要不停地称赞我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}やまがはに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溅溅山溪淌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作要更快更直接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}やくやもしほの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卤水釜中沸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}よのなかは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事应有定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あまのをぶねの つなでかなしも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远观纤拉人 百感九回肠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ありあけの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰看无情月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あかつきばかり うきものはなし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断肠唯此时 拂晓与君别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原上采春芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要叫你新 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在一起玩歌牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさ はなさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满院非 满院非
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそ はなさそふ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满院非白 满院非白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふりゆくものは わがみなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过眼云烟散 身老叹韶华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害 真岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考上开明成 真的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说真岛同学考上开明成中学了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他的第一志愿不是秀西大附属吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能骑着自行车去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哪个笨蛋考上开明成还去秀西大附属的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要花一个半钟头去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 你不会去那学校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则就不能去老师那里玩歌牌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能玩歌牌我也要去开明成 这不是明摆着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 新
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一竟然说不能一起玩歌牌也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 在福井的爷爷病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业之后我就要回福井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一直在一起玩歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爷爷没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是脑溢血 还在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病的不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去…不去比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 今天千早怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说是我的错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我要回福井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不去歌牌大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她相处的时间比你长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下我一个人话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌一点乐趣都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个得还给老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 睫毛君不是很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考上开明成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是每个礼拜来歌牌会就能考上的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没看见吗 真不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 眼镜君的爷爷是歌牌的永世名人 很厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜君有他爷爷的教导才能那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷病倒之后他该有多么的担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分 老师 真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你都不来的话 我会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是要跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是我出钱你写字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道千早会不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这么小型的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 第一场对阵的胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是全国大赛的第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在跟他比大概赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来开始第一场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真岛同学跟戴眼镜的孩子一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}千早振留队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 他们好像说今天要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是循环赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只要他们两个赢了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是决心今天一定要打败绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你们的队友是怕输才不来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早只是迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了她会来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输给我之后就给你买肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太晚了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为道口要等20分钟才开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个只把我一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是寂寞的不止是我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下因幡道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはがた みじかきあしの ふしのまも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短芦苇节 难波满海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牌在不断减少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牌只有一百张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一 真想把奖杯给千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我能赢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早也说句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想 还想三个人一起玩歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小千 要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开明成的西装…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小千 下一张跟我们拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新 妈妈去跟房东道别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去把打包行李
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天就搬家了 你自己的东西也要打包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新 你怎么能一个人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我玩歌牌吧 新
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真地决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忙着整理？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算对手只有5岁 我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはづに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花开难波津
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太一你读的好死板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读牌要按照4-3-1-5的方式来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停顿方法是吧 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いにしへの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都奈良城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わすらるる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誓遭遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かぜをいたみ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风急波浪涌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了 赢的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有录音带 录音带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是当上歌牌名人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟 我是因为与新相遇才爱上歌牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说如果同时拿到由歌牌所在方为胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的「千早」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起…玩歌牌 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早和太一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大概我们再也见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有歌牌在 还会再见面的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持下去就还能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.42,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.90,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:34.11,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.57,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:48.15,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:55.96,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.36,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:07.02,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.89,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:16.81,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.42,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}慢步走过回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.90,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}微风轻轻吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:34.11,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}闲话家常也异常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}至今依旧一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.57,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们常常相约等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:48.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可否仍然记得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:55.96,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在我心怀强烈的向往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有什么在目标之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:07.02,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}现在的话似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.89,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}试着伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:16.81,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在梦想的路上终有一天会再度重逢吧
